    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Pale Maw veterans are long-serving members of the Entropy cult — scarred, weathered warriors who have survived campaigns that killed their fellows. They move with the quiet confidence of survivors, keeping Defensive Posture alongside allies and hitting with the Veteran's Thrust that exploits any opening. Their Experienced feature gives them an uncanny ability to read enemy tactics before the attack lands. They are reference-quality opponents — not commonly deployed, but devastating when they are.</p>",
